      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and making sure it runs like a dream. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy that 'new car' magic. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
